---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Accessibility Statement"
  description="Our commitment to digital accessibility and WCAG 2.1 Level AA conformance."
>
  <style>
    .a11y-wrap {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, sans-serif;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.7;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .a11y-wrap h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    .a11y-wrap h2 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 2.25rem 0 0.6rem;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    .a11y-wrap p { margin: 0 0 1rem; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #1f2937; }
    .a11y-wrap ul { margin: 0 0 1rem 1.25rem; padding: 0; }
    .a11y-wrap li { margin: 0.25rem 0; font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #1f2937; }
    .a11y-wrap a { color: #1d4ed8; text-decoration: underline; }
    .a11y-wrap a:hover { color: #1e40af; }
    .a11y-meta {
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1.25rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .a11y-back {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      min-height: 44px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .a11y-back:hover { background: #1e293b; }
  </style>
  <div class="a11y-wrap">
    <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
    <p>
      <strong>Template:</strong> dcrader-template-pets
    </p>
    <p>
      This template is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people of all
      abilities. We strive to conform to <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> standards
      and continuously improve the user experience for everyone. We design and build
      to be perceivable, operable, understandable, and robust for visitors using
      assistive technology, including screen readers, keyboard navigation, screen
      magnification, and voice control.
    </p>

    <h2>Our commitment</h2>
    <p>
      We work to meet WCAG 2.1 Level AA across every page of this template,
      including descriptive alternative text, sufficient color contrast, visible
      focus indicators, labelled form fields, keyboard-operable navigation, and
      reduced-motion support.
    </p>

    <h2>Feedback &amp; contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you experience any difficulty accessing this site, please contact us at
      <a href="mailto:accessibility@dcrader.dev">accessibility@dcrader.dev</a>.
      We aim to respond to accessibility feedback within 5 business days.
    </p>

    <h2>Measures taken</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Descriptive alternative text for all meaningful images.</li>
      <li>Color contrast of at least 4.5:1 for body text and 3:1 for large text and UI components.</li>
      <li>Visible focus indicators on every interactive element.</li>
      <li>Labelled form fields and helpful error messages.</li>
      <li>Skip-to-content link and logical heading structure on every page.</li>
      <li>Touch targets sized for finger and assistive-pointer use.</li>
      <li>Reduced-motion support for visitors who prefer minimal animation.</li>
      <li>Keyboard-operable navigation, menus, and dialogs.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="a11y-meta">
      Last updated: <strong>2026-05-17</strong>
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="a11y-back">Back to home</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
